puts it somewhere.

02:36.000 --> 02:37.100
Hides it somewhere.

02:37.100 --> 02:40.100
But, honey, you've dreamt
this dream how many times now?

02:40.600 --> 02:41.600
I mean, after a while,

02:41.600 --> 02:44.700
don't you start
to get a little... desensitized?

02:44.800 --> 02:46.700
No, I don't.
