to have a conversation with the late Mrs. Paxton.

02:51.300 --> 02:54.200
Explain to her
there may be other dead people

02:54.200 --> 02:55.400
who need your help,

02:55.600 --> 02:57.800
and she can't be monopolizing
your dreamtime like this.

02:57.800 --> 03:00.300
Yeah? Well, next time
I see her, I'll tell her.

03:00.300 --> 03:06.200
Right after I ask her where her loving husband
stashed her head.

