Oh, no, that'd
be awful.

05:09.100 --> 05:11.300
Okay, guys, come on,
finish your cereal.

05:11.300 --> 05:12.600
I gotta go talk to Daddy.

05:18.700 --> 05:19.700
Hey.

05:20.900 --> 05:21.600
Help me out here.

05:21.600 --> 05:24.800
Which, which one
of these shirts looks the most
