05:39.200 --> 05:40.900
Pretty excited about going
to the therapist, huh?

05:40.900 --> 05:42.500
Oh, yeah. Huh?

05:46.000 --> 05:47.700
Well, you want some company?

05:48.200 --> 05:50.300
Going to the company-
ordered shrink?

05:50.400 --> 05:51.600
Well, yeah, I could drive you.

05:51.600 --> 05:53.100
You know, wait with you.

05:53.100 --> 05:55.500
Who knows? Maybe he'll even
let me come in with you.

05:55.500 --> 05:56.700
Al, I can do this.

05:56.700 --> 05:58.800
I appreciate the offer,
but I can do this.

05:58.800 --> 06:00.600
No. I know you can.

06:00.700 --> 06:02.100
You're worried
about me. I get it.

06:02.100 --> 06:05.700
And I appreciate it, but
I'll be fine. I <i>am</i> fine.

06:06.900 --> 06:08.000
You know, I think
they're right.

06:08.000 --> 06:10.500
Maybe I went back
to work too soon,

06:11.000 --> 06:14.600
so if they want me to go
talk to this guy, 
